<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Our catering offers fresh, tasty, and nutritious food for any occasion.">
    <title>Keamo's Catering</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Keamo's Catering</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#about">About Us</a>
            <a href="#menu">Menu</a>
            <a href="#Bookings">Booking</a>
            <a href="#contact-us">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to Keamo's catering services where your events are brought to life with custom-tailored menus and exceptional service.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="menu">
            <h2>Our Menu</h2>
            <p>We offer diverse catering options. Explore our menus below:</p>

            <h3>Meat Menu</h3>
            <a href="meat.html">
                <img src="images/meat.jpeg" alt="Assorted grilled meats served with sides">
            </a>

            <h3>Finger Snacks</h3>
            <a href="fingersnacks.html">
                <img src="images/fingersnacks.jpeg" alt="Assorted finger snacks perfect for parties">
            </a>

            <h3>Platters</h3>
            <a href="platters.html">
                <img src="images/platters.jpeg" alt="Colorful party platters with variety">
            </a>
        </section>

        <section id="contact-us">
            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>If you have any queries, please reach out to us:</p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@keamoscatering.co.za">info@keamoscatering.co.za</a></p>
            <p>Phone: +27 79 358 7567</p>
            <p>Location: Johannesburg, South Africa</p>
        </section>

        <section id="Bookings">
            <h2>Book Us</h2>
            <p>Fill in the form below to book us:</p>
            <form action="" method="POST">
                <label for="name">Full Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name"><br><br>

                <label for="email">Email Address:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email"><br><br>

                <label for="event">Select Event:</label>
                <select id="event" name="event">
                    <option value="">--Please choose an event--</option>
                    <option value="wedding">Wedding</option>
                    <option value="kidsparty">Kid's Party</option>
                    <option value="workshop">Workshop</option>
                    <option value="conference">Business Conference</option>
                </select><br><br>

                <label for="date">Event Date:</label>
                <input type="date" id="date" name="date"><br><br>

                <label for="people">Number of People:</label>
                <input type="number" id="people" name="people" min="5"><br><br>

                <label for="message">Additional Message or Requests:</label><br>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" cols="50"></textarea><br><br>

                <input type="submit" value="Book Now">
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>Â© 2025 Keamo's Catering | All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
